In this article, Vice President Pence introduces President Trump at his first event at the CIA headquarters. Pence expresses his gratitude for the opportunity to serve and acknowledges the sacrifices made by the intelligence community. He praises Trump's dedication to the safety and security of the United States and his strategic thinking. Trump then speaks, expressing his support for the intelligence community and emphasizing the importance of eradicating ISIS. He introduces Mike Pompeo as the new CIA Director and praises his qualifications. Trump also criticizes the media for their dishonesty and recounts incidents where they misrepresented facts. He concludes by expressing his confidence in the intelligence community and his belief that they will help make America safe and successful again.